'''''Neoregelia fluminensis''''' is a [[species (biology)|species]] of the [[genus (biology)|genus]] ''[[Neoregelia]]''. This species is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Brazil]].

==Cultivars==
* [[Neoregelia Heat Wave|''Neoregelia'' 'Heat Wave']]
* [[Neoregelia Rust Belt Special|''Neoregelia'' 'Rust Belt Special']]

